ד און ליין\"><img src=\"/images/thumb/8/8c/%D7%A1%D7%99_%D7%90%D7%95_%D7%90%D7%9C_%D7%A1%D7%9E%D7%9C%D7%99%D7%9C.jpg/15px-%D7%A1%D7%99_%D7%90%D7%95_%D7%90%D7%9C_%D7%A1%D7%9E%D7%9C%D7%99%D7%9C.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" class=\"mw-file-element\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/8/8c/%D7%A1%D7%99_%D7%90%D7%95_%D7%90%D7%9C_%D7%A1%D7%9E%D7%9C%D7%99%D7%9C.jpg/23px-%D7%A1%D7%99_%D7%90%D7%95_%D7%90%D7%9C_%D7%A1%D7%9E%D7%9C%D7%99%D7%9C.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/8/8c/%D7%A1%D7%99_%D7%90%D7%95_%D7%90%D7%9C_%D7%A1%D7%9E%D7%9C%D7%99%D7%9C.jpg/30px-%D7%A1%D7%99_%D7%90%D7%95_%D7%90%D7%9C_%D7%A1%D7%9E%D7%9C%D7%99%D7%9C.jpg 2x\" /></a></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">^</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">יודי, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://chabad.info/news/356527/\">כינוס תורה בכולל אברכים שע\"י קהילת חב\"ד לוד</a> <span typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"/index.php/%D7%97%D7%91%22%D7%93_%D7%90%D7%99%D7%A0%D7%A4%D7%95\" title=\"חב&quot;ד אינפו\"><img src=\"/images/thumb/e/ec/%D7%90%D7%99%D7%A0%D7%A4%D7%95.jpg/27px-%D7%90%D7%99%D7%A0%D7%A4%D7%95.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"27\" height=\"9\" class=\"mw-file-element\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/e/ec/%D7%90%D7%99%D7%A0%D7%A4%D7%95.jpg/41px-%D7%90%D7%99%D7%A0%D7%A4%D7%95.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/e/ec/%D7%90%D7%99%D7%A0%D7%A4%D7%95.jpg/54px-%D7%90%D7%99%D7%A0%D7%A4%D7%95.jpg 2x\" /></a></span> כ\"ה ניסן תשע\"ח.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">^</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://chabad.info/news/666632/\">לוד: כינוס תורה בבית המדרש \"מעייני הישועה – ליובאוויטש\"</a> <span typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"/index.php/%D7%97%D7%91%22%D7%93_%D7%90%D7%99%D7%A0%D7%A4%D7%95\" title=\"חב&quot;ד אינפו\"><img src=\"/images/thumb/e/ec/%D7%90%D7%99%D7%A0%D7%A4%D7%95.jpg/27px-%D7%90%D7%99%D7%A0%D7%A4%D7%95.jpg\" decod